      <section eId="sec_9_10_4">
        <num>9-10-4</num>
        <content>
          <p>All collateral issues in the superior, state, or city courts, unless otherwise directed by law, shall be tried by jury.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 3532; Code 1868, § 3555; Code 1873, § 3612; Code 1882, § 3612; Civil Code 1895, § 4948; Civil Code 1910, § 5525; Code 1933, § 81-1010.)</p>
